How have you been recently? I started new work.
There's no guarantee that everything will go accordingly.

BUT

I believe myself.
Everything is going to be alright.
I hope it will be a fantastic year.

AND

 I hope that something wonderful will come to you too.

THANKS



Canvas size：A4
Resolution：350 dpi

------------------------------------------------------------

I have a dream.
I want to artwork with my favorite artist.
But, I am an unrecognized Japanese illustrator.
I have to be famous.

What do you think about this work？
If you like this work, You will make my dreams come true soon.

Thanks.
